    Contains the post messages for each SBMLError in the French language.

    'post' mean that this is added at the end of the generic error message defined in the SBMLErrorMessage bundle. This part of the error has, in general, several parameters to be able to customize the message to provide some information about which element contained the error and why the error was raised.

    The key for each post message is the integer defined for each SBMLError in SBMLErrorCodes.
